Star Wars fans were treated to a trip of a lifetime on board the first ever R2-D ANA JET passenger flight. 
The fans - who dressed up for the occasion - enjoyed a flight on the special Star Wars themed All Nippon Airways plane over Haneda, Tokyo. 
When the themed- Boeing 787-9 Dreamliner was announced in April 2015, ANA said they were using the aircraft as a way to "enhance its international presence". All Nippon Airways
